pan><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">將</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">快</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">速</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">盤</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">活</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">核</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">心</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">存</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">量</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">資</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">產，積</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">極</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">踐</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">行「好</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">房</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">子」建</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">設</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">理</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">念</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">與「好</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">生</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">活」營</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">造</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">目</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">標，在</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">切</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">實</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">保</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">障</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">主</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">實</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">現「安</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">居</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">樂</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業」的</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">民</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">生</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">事</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">上</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">再</span><span 